      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a id=\"scale\"&gt;</ph> <ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>Designing your Application for Scale"
    },
    {
      "content": "Sometimes, you may want to take a single application (like a simple web",
      "pos": [
        8182,
