        11298
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "queue allows you to scale the number of Web Site role instances",
      "pos": [
        11299,
        11362
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "independently of the Order Processing role instances.",
      "pos": [
        11363,
        11416
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This is very",
      "pos": [
