      ],
      "content": "<ph id=\"ph1\">&lt;a id=\"defandcfg\"&gt;</ph> <ph id=\"ph2\">&lt;/a&gt;</ph>Hosted Service Definition and Configuration"
    },
    {
      "content": "Deploying a hosted service to Azure requires you to also have a",
